#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid "&keurocalc; is an universal pocket currency converter and calculator."
msgstr "&keurocalc; je univerzalni džepni konvertor i kalkulator za valute."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the 1st of January, 2002, 12 European countries united their national "
"currencies into a single one, the euro (€). The same happens from time to "
"time on a smaller scale with new European countries. &keurocalc; helps:"
msgstr ""
"Prvog januara 2002., 12 europskih zemalja je ujedinilo svoje nacionalne "
"valute u jednu, euro (€). Isto se dešava s vremena na vrijeme u manjem "
"opsegu sa novim europskim zemljama. &keurocalc; pomaže:"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid "During the transition periods"
msgstr "Tokom perioda tranzicije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To verify one's bank account, when paying both in euros and in the old "
"currency (Italian liras, for example)."
msgstr ""
"Za provjeru nečijeg bankovnog računa, kada plaća u i eurima i u staroj "
"valuti (Italijanskim lirama, na primjer)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To verify one's shopping, and compute the change if paying with a banknote "
"labeled in the old currency."
msgstr ""
"Za provjeru nečije kupovine, i računanje razlike ukoliko se plaća novčanicom "
"označenom starom valutom."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid "Many years after the transition periods"
msgstr "Monogo godina nakon perioda tranzicije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To get an idea of the value of the things in the old currency at any stage "
"of calculations."
msgstr ""
"Za stvaranje ideje o vrijednostima stvari u staroj valuti u bilokojoj fazi "
"računanja."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid "At any time"
msgstr "U bilo koje vrijeme"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To do conversions between the euro and other currencies, like the British "
"Pound, according to the daily exchange rate published by the <ulink url="
"\"http://www.ecb.int/stats/eurofxref/\">European Central Bank (ECB)</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Za konvergenciju eura i drugih valuta, kao što je britanska funta, prema "
"dnevnom kursu koji objavljuje <ulink url=\"http://www.ecb.int/stats/"
"eurofxref/\">European Central Bank (ECB)</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To do conversions between any two currencies that are part of the list "
"published by the ECB."
msgstr ""
"Za konvergenciju bilo koje dvije valute koje su dio liste Europske Centralne "
"Banke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To do conversions between the euro and other currencies, like the British "
"Pound, according to the daily exchange rate published by the <ulink url="
"\"http://rss.timegenie.com/foreign_exchange_rates_forex\">Time Genie</ulink> "
"foreign exchange (TG)."
msgstr ""
"Za konvergenciju eura i drugih valuta, kao što je britanska funta, prema "
"dnevnom kursu koji objavljuje  the <ulink url=\"http://rss.timegenie.com/"
"foreign_exchange_rates_forex\">Time Genie</ulink> foreign exchange (TG)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To do conversions between any two currencies that are part of the list "
"published by the TG."
msgstr ""
"Za konvergenciju bilo koje dvije valute koje su dio liste koju objavljuje TG."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&keurocalc; has the following advantages in term of comfort and usability:"
msgstr ""
"&keurocalc; ima sljedeće prednosti u smislu udobnosti i upotrebljivosti:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You see every intermediate value and the result in both the reference "
"currency (euro) and in the other currency."
msgstr ""
"Vidite svaku srednju vrijednost i rezultat i u referentnoj valuti (euro) i u "
"drugoj valuti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There is a separate input area where you can type a new value while still "
"having the previous result visible."
msgstr ""
"Postoji poseban ulaz gdje možete upisati novu vrijednost dok je još uvijek "
"prethodni rezultat vidljiv."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The ergonomy is very close to usual pocket calculators, despite the fact "
"that any value you type can be a value in the reference currency (euro), a "
"value in the other currency, a percentage or an unit-less quantity."
msgstr ""
"Ergonomija je vrlo blizu uobičajenim džepnim kalkulatorima, uprkos činjenici "
"da bilo koja vrijednost koju upišete može biti vrijednost u referentnoj "
"valuti (euro), vrijednost u nekoj drugoj valuti, postotak ili jedinica manje "
"količine."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You press the keys in the order you would speak aloud what you're doing."
msgstr "Pritišćete tipke redoslijedom kojim biste naglas govorili šta radite."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you make mistakes, a special correction button enables you to correct "
"your last input data, as long as you didn't validate."
msgstr ""
"Ukoliko pogriješite, posebno dugme za korekciju vam omogućava da ispravite "
"svoj posljednji unos, sve dok niste potvrdili."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The numbers are displayed according to your locale settings: with either a "
"comma or a dot as a decimal point, according to your &systemsettings; "
"settings."
msgstr ""
"Brojevi su prikazani u skladu s vašim lokalnim postavkama: sa decimalnim "
"zarezom ili sa decimalnom tačkom, u skladu s vašim &systemsettings; "
"postavkama."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can decide where &keurocalc; should download the conversion rates from, "
"which currency to start with when you launch &keurocalc;, and which rounding "
"method to use."
msgstr ""
"Možete odlučiti odakle &keurocalc; treba preuzeti stope konverzije, u kojoj "
"valuti da se počnete kada pokrenete &keurocalc;, i koju metodu zaokruživanja "
"da koristi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid "&keurocalc; allows the following operations:"
msgstr "&keurocalc; dozvoljava slijedeće operacije:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid "Conversions from and to the reference currency (euro)."
msgstr "Konvergenciju u i iz referentne valute (euro)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Systematic rounding of the displayed result, but computations done "
"internally with the precision of the mathematical libraries."
msgstr ""
"Sistematsko zaokruživanje prikazanih rezultata, ali proračune vrši interno s "
"preciznošću matematičke biblioteka."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid "Usual additions, subtractions, multiplications and divisions."
msgstr "Uobičajna sabiranja, oduzimanja, množenja i dijeljenja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid "Apply a percentage, add a percentage, or subtract a percentage."
msgstr "Primjenjivanje postotka, dodavanje postotka, ili oduzimanje postotka."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Possibility to store values in an intermediate memory, or use that memory as "
"a running total."
msgstr ""
"Mogućnost za čuvanje vrijednosti u srednjoj memoriji, ili korištenje te "
"memorije za ukupno pokretanje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:152
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here are some limitations of &keurocalc;:"
msgstr "Evo nekih ograničenja &keurocalc;:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid "No parenthesized or complex expressions."
msgstr "Ne podržava zagrade ili složenije izraze."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:156
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some roundings go wrong due to the limitations of the mathematical library."
msgstr ""
"Neka zaokruživanja ne budu ispravna zbog ograničenosti matematičke "
"biblioteke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:158
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Inflationist currencies cannot be handled due to limited display size. "
"However, with the change to the new Turkish lira and the removal of six "
"zeroes in that currency, it is not a practical problem anymore."
msgstr ""
"Ne može se rukovati inflatornim valutama zbog ograničene veličine ekrana. "
"Međutim, s promjenom u novu tursku liru i uklanjanjem šest nula u toj "
"valuti, to više nije praktičan problem."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&keurocalc; never guarantees the exactness of the exchange rates nor the "
"accuracy of the result. You are always invited to verify your computations "
"by some other means. As the <link linkend=\"credits\">license</link> "
"agreement states, there's no liability of the authors if the results are not "
"correct or as expected. Also, please notice that the variable exchange rates "
"are downloaded in an unencrypted and therefore insecure manner from the data "
"sources (European Central Bank and Time Genie). Some <quote>man-in-the-"
"middle</quote> attacker may confuse &keurocalc; by forging exchange rates. "
"More simply, a transmission error is always possible."
msgstr ""
"&keurocalc; ne garantuje nikada za tačnost kursa niti rezultata.Uvijek ste "
"pozvani da potvrdite svoju proračune nekim drugim sredstvima. Kao što <link "
"linkend=\"credits\">licenca</link> ugovor iznosi, autor ne snosi odgovornost "
"ukoliko rezultati nisu ispravni ili onakvi kakvi su očekivani. Također, "
"molim vas da primjetite da je varijabla kursa skinuta u nešifriranom obliku, "
"te je zbog toga nesigurna vrsta izvora podataka(European Central Bank i Time "
"Genie). Neki <quote>man-in-the-middle</quote> napadač može zbuniti "
"&keurocalc; sa stranim kursevima. Jednostavnije, greška prenosa je uvijek "
"moguća."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &keurocalc;"
msgstr "Korištenje &keurocalc;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid "Performing Conversions"
msgstr "Izvođenje konvergencije"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid "To convert 1000 Belgian francs into euros"
msgstr "Za konvergenciju 1000 belgijskih franaka u eure"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the <guilabel>BEF - Belgian franc</guilabel> (<foreignphrase>francs "
"belges</foreignphrase>) item in the currencies drop down list on the bottom. "
"If that choice is not available, press the <guibutton>Settings...</"
"guibutton> button and select <guilabel>Euro, no network access (fixed rates "
"only)</guilabel> to make the correct rates list appear."
msgstr ""
"Odaberite <guilabel>BEF - Belgijski frank</guilabel> (<foreignphrase>francs "
"belges</foreignphrase>) stavku u listi valuta na dnu. Ako taj odabir nije "
"dostupan, pritisnite <guibutton>Postavke...</guibutton> dugme i odaberite "
"<guilabel>Euro, nema pristupa mreži (samo fiksne stope)</guilabel> kako bi "
"se pojavila lista ispravne stope."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:198
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Type <userinput>1000</userinput> on the keyboard or use the corresponding "
"numerical buttons. The digits appear while you are typing them in the "
"<guilabel>Input</guilabel> display. If you make a mistake while typing the "
"digits use the &Backspace; key or the <guibutton>&lt;-</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Ukucajte <userinput>1000</userinput> na tastaturi li koristite odgovarajuću "
"numeričku dugmad. Cifre se pojavljuju dok ih kucate u <guilabel>Ulaz</"
"guilabel> zaslonu. Ukoliko napravite pogrešku dok kucate cifre iskoristite "
"&Backspace; tipku ili <guibutton>&lt;-</guibutton> dugme."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:202
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press the <guibutton>FB</guibutton> button or the <keycap>F</keycap> key. In "
"fact, any key that is not already reserved for some other usage will "
"validate the input as a number expressed in the currency, so <keycap>B</"
"keycap> or <keycap>X</keycap> would have worked as well."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite <guibutton>FB</guibutton> dugme ili <keycap>F</keycap> tipku. U "
"stvari, bilo koji ključ koji nije već rezervisan za neku drugu upotrebu će "
"potvrditi ulazne podatke kao broj izražen u valuti, tako da bi<keycap>B</"
"keycap> ili <keycap>X</keycap> isto tako radili."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:206
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Read the result in the <guilabel>Result</guilabel> display on the right: "
"24.79 € or 24,79 € according to our locale settings."
msgstr ""
"Pročitajte rezultat u <guilabel>Rezultat</guilabel> zaslonu desno: 24.79 € "
"ili 24,79 € ovisno od veših lokalnih postavki."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid "To convert 25 euros into Belgian francs"
msgstr "Za konvergenciju 25 eura u belgijske franke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:212
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the fixed rates currencies are available, select the <guilabel>BEF - "
"Belgian franc</guilabel> item in the currencies drop down list on the "
"bottom. You can skip this step if it's already the selected currency."
msgstr ""
"Ukoliko su dostupne fiksne stope valuta, odaberite <guilabel>BEF - Belgijski "
"frank</guilabel> stavku u listi valuta na dnu. Ovaj korak možete preskočiti "
"ako je već odabrana ova valuta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:216
#, no-c-format
msgid "Type <userinput>25</userinput>."
msgstr "Ukucajte <userinput>25</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:217
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press the <guibutton>€</guibutton> button or the <keycap>E</keycap> key."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite <guibutton>€</guibutton> dugme ili <keycap>E</keycap> tipku."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:219
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Read the result in the <guilabel>Result</guilabel> display on the right: "
"1008.50 FB or 1008,50 FB. The exact value is 1008.4975, but it's rounded to "
"the closest hundredth of a Belgian franc. The rounding unit depends on the "
"currency and on the rounding method: with the official rounding rules, for "
"Belgian francs it's 0.01 FB, for Italian liras it's 1 L for example."
msgstr ""
"Pročitajte rezultat na <guilabel>Rezultat</guilabel> zaslonu desno: 1008.50 "
"FB ili 1008,50 FB. Tačna vrijednost je 1008.4975, ali je zaokružena na "
"najbliže stotinke belgijskog franka. Jedinica zaokruživanja ovisi od valute "
"i metode zaokruživanja: prema zvaničnim pravilima zaokruživanja, na primjer "
"za begijske franke je 0.01 FB, za talijanske lire je 1 L."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:226
#, no-c-format
msgid "You could also have typed: <userinput>25 Enter E</userinput>."
msgstr "Također ste mogli ukucati: <userinput>25 Enter E</userinput>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:229
#, no-c-format
msgid "To convert 120 German marks into Spanish pesetas"
msgstr "Za konvergenciju 120 njemačkih maraka u španske pasete"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:230
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the fixed rates currencies are available, select the <guilabel>DEM - "
"German deutschmark</guilabel> item in the currencies drop down list."
msgstr ""
"Ukoliko su dostupne fiksne stope valuta, odaberite <guilabel>DEM - njemačka "
"marka</guilabel> stavku u listi valuta ispod."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid "Type <userinput>120</userinput>."
msgstr "Ukucajte <userinput>120</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:234
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press the <guibutton>DM</guibutton> button or the <keycap>D</keycap> or "
"<keycap>M</keycap> keys."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite <guibutton>DM</guibutton> dugme ili <keycap>D</keycap> ili "
"<keycap>M</keycap> tipke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Just select the <guilabel>ESP - Spanish peseta</guilabel> item to see the "
"same amount of 61.36 € converted into pesetas in the <guilabel>Result</"
"guilabel> area."
msgstr ""
"Samo odaberite<guilabel>ESP - Španska paseta</guilabel> stavku da vidite "
"isti iznos od 61.36 € konvertovan u pasete u <guilabel>Rezultat</guilabel> "
"području."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:244
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding and Subtracting"
msgstr "Sabiranje i oduzimanje"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:247
#, no-c-format
msgid "How much is 3 + 5?"
msgstr "Koliko je 3 + 5?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:248
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Type <userinput>3</userinput> and then press <guibutton>+</guibutton>. "
"Notice that in the result field, <computeroutput>3</computeroutput> is a "
"simple value displayed on just one line, with no monetary unit."
msgstr ""
"Ukucajte <userinput>3</userinput> i onda pritisnite <guibutton>+</"
"guibutton>. Primijetite u polju za rezultat, <computeroutput>3</"
"computeroutput> je obična vrijednost prikazana u jednoj liniji, bez "
"monetarne jedinice."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:251
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Type <userinput>5</userinput> and then press the <guibutton>Enter</"
"guibutton> button or the &Enter; key. The result <computeroutput>8</"
"computeroutput> appears on the right."
msgstr ""
"Ukucajte <userinput>5</userinput> i onda pritisnite <guibutton>Enter</"
"guibutton> dugme ili &Enter; tipku. Rezultat <computeroutput>8</"
"computeroutput> se pojavljuje na desnoj strani."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:257
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You received 100 US dollars and paid 32.50 euros for a book, how much do you "
"have left in your bank account?"
msgstr ""
"Primili ste 100 američkih dolara i platili 32.50 eura za knjigu, koliko vam "
"je ostalo na bankovnom računu?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:259
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Make sure that the variable exchange rates are available. If not, press the "
"<guibutton>Settings...</guibutton> to select either <guilabel>Euro, European "
"Central Bank</guilabel> or <guilabel>Euro, Time Genie</guilabel>. Now select "
"the <guilabel>USD - US dollar</guilabel> item in the scroll down list on the "
"bottom. If you have no Internet access, that item won't be available as the "
"latest variable rates between the euro and the dollar cannot be determined."
msgstr ""
"Pobrinite se da su kursevi dostupni. Ukoliko nisu, pritisnite "
"<guibutton>Postavke...</guibutton> kako biste odabrali ili <guilabel>Euro, "
"European Central Bank</guilabel> ili <guilabel>Euro, Time Genie</guilabel>. "
"Sada odaberite <guilabel>USD - US dollar</guilabel> stavku u listi. Ako "
"nemate pristup internetu, ta stavka neće biti dostupna kako se ne mogu "
"utvrditi najnovije varijabilne stope između eura i dolara."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:268
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Type <userinput>100</userinput> and then press <guibutton>$</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Ukucajte <userinput>100</userinput> i onda pritisnite <guibutton>$</"
"guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:269
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press the <guibutton>-</guibutton> button or the <keycap>-</keycap> key. "
"Notice the <computeroutput>-</computeroutput> sign in the leftmost part of "
"the <guilabel>Input</guilabel> display."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite <guibutton>-</guibutton> dugme ili <keycap>-</keycap> tipku. "
"Primijetite <computeroutput>-</computeroutput> znak u krajnjem lijevom "
"dijelu <guilabel>Input</guilabel> zaslona."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:272
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Type <userinput>32,50</userinput> or <userinput>32.50</userinput> and then "
"press <guibutton>€</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Ukucajte <userinput>32,50</userinput> ili <userinput>32.50</userinput> i "
"onda pritisnite <guibutton>€</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:274
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Read the result in the <guilabel>Result</guilabel> display on the right. The "
"exact value might depend on latest exchange rates. Notice that during the "
"whole computation you've been able to read the values both in euro and in US "
"dollars. Pay attention to the fact that different data sources (ECB or TG) "
"might not provide the same conversion rate between the euro and the dollar."
msgstr ""
"Pročitajte rezultat na <guilabel>Rezultat</guilabel> zaslonu desno. Tačna "
"vrijednost bi mogla ovisiti od najnovije kursne liste. Primijetite da ste "
"tijekom cijelog računanja u mogućnosti da čitate vrijednosti, kako u eurima "
"tako i u američkim dolarima. Obratite pažnju na činjenicu da različiti "
"izvori podataka (ECB ili TG) možda neće pružiti istu stopu konverzije između "
"eura i dolara."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:282
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You pay a 32.50 € book with a 500 FF banknote. How much was the clerk "
"supposed to give you back, in euro notes and coins?"
msgstr ""
"Platili ste knjigu od 32,50 € sa 500 FF novčanicom. Koliko bi službenik "
"trebao da vam vrati, u novčanicama i kovanicama eura?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:284
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the <guilabel>FRF - French francs</guilabel> item in the currencies "
"drop down list if not already selected."
msgstr ""
"Odaberite <guilabel>FRF - Francuski franci</guilabel> stavka u listi valuta "
"ukoliko već nije odabrano."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:286
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Type <userinput>32.50</userinput> or <userinput>32,50</userinput> and then "
"press <guibutton>€</guibutton>. You can also type <userinput>32.5</"
"userinput> without the trailing <userinput>0</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Ukucajte <userinput>32.50</userinput> ili <userinput>32,50</userinput> i "
"onda pritisnite <guibutton>€</guibutton>. Također možete ukucati "
"<userinput>32.5</userinput> bez <userinput>0</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:289
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press the <guibutton>-</guibutton> button or the <keycap>-</keycap> key."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite <guibutton>-</guibutton> dugme ili <keycap>-</keycap> tipku."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:290
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Type <userinput>500</userinput> and press the <guibutton>FF</guibutton> "
"button or the <keycap>F</keycap> key."
msgstr ""
"Ukucajte <userinput>500</userinput> i pritisnite <guibutton>FF</guibutton> "
"dugme ili <keycap>F</keycap> tipku."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:292
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The result <computeroutput>-43.72 €</computeroutput> is negative, indicating "
"that change money has to be given back to the customer. The <guibutton>+/-</"
"guibutton> button or the <keycap>S</keycap> key permit you to change the "
"sign of the result."
msgstr ""
"Rezultat <computeroutput>-43.72 €</computeroutput> je negaivan,ukazuje da bi "
"kusur trebao biti vraćen kupcu. <guibutton>+/-</guibutton> dugme ili "
"<keycap>S</keycap> tipka vam dozvoljavaju da promjenite predznak rezultata."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:297
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Do not try to add euros to simple values (with no currency unit): it won't "
"work, for the same reason you cannot add 5 meters to 3 kilograms."
msgstr ""
"Nemojte pokušati dodati eure na jednostavne vrijednosti (bez valute): to "
"neće raditi, iz istog razloga iz kojeg ne možete dodati 5 metara na 3 "
"kilograma."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:303
#, no-c-format
msgid "Multiplying and Dividing"
msgstr "Množenje i dijeljenje"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:306
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You buy 3.2 kilograms of apples at 2 € per kilogram. How much does the whole "
"cost in Australian dollars?"
msgstr ""
"Kupujete 3.2 kilograma jabuka od 2 € po kilogramu. Koliko cijeli trošak "
"iznosi u australijskim dolarima?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:308
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the <guilabel>AUD - Australian dollar</guilabel> item if available "
"and if not already selected."
msgstr ""
"Odaberite <guilabel>AUD - Australijski dolar</guilabel> stavku ukoliko je "
"dostupna i nije već odabrana."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:310
#, no-c-format
msgid "Type <userinput>2</userinput> and press <guibutton>€</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Ukucajte <userinput>2</userinput> i pritisnite <guibutton>€</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:311
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press the <guibutton>X</guibutton> button or the <keycap>*</keycap> key. "
"Notice the <computeroutput>X</computeroutput> sign at the left of the "
"<guilabel>Input</guilabel> display."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite <guibutton>X</guibutton> dugme na <keycap>*</keycap> tipku. "
"Primijetite <computeroutput>X</computeroutput> znak na lijevoj strani "
"<guilabel>Input</guilabel> zaslona."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:314
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now type <userinput>3.2</userinput> followed by the <guibutton>Enter</"
"guibutton> button or the &Enter; key: this means <quote>3.2 units</quote> at "
"2 € each."
msgstr ""
"Sada ukucajte <userinput>3.2</userinput> zatim pritisnite <guibutton>Enter</"
"guibutton> dugme &Enter; tipku: ovo znači <quote>3.2 jedinice</quote> po 2 € "
"svaka."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:317
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The result in Australian dollars matches <computeroutput>6.4 €</"
"computeroutput>."
msgstr ""
"Rezultat u austarlijskim dolarima odgovara<computeroutput>6.4 €</"
"computeroutput>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:320
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You could also have used the following order: <userinput>3.2 = * 2 €</"
"userinput> or even <userinput>3.2 * 2 €</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Također ste mogli koristiti slijedeću naredbu: <userinput>3.2 = * 2 €</"
"userinput> ili čak <userinput>3.2 * 2 €</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:323
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It's not possible to multiply X euros by Y dollars, just as you don't "
"multiply 10 fingers by 2 ears."
msgstr ""
"Nije moguće pomnožiti X eura sa Y dolara, baš kao što ne možete pomnožiti 10 "
"prstiju sa 2 uha."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:330
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using Percentages"
msgstr "Upotreba procenta"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:333
#, no-c-format
msgid "How much is 20% of 3000 yen?"
msgstr "Koliko je 20% od 3000 jena?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:334 index.docbook:346 index.docbook:360
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the <guilabel>JPY - Japanese yen</guilabel> item if available and if "
"not already selected."
msgstr ""
"Odaberite <guilabel>JPY - Japanski jen</guilabel> stavku ukoliko je dostupna "
"i nije već odabrana."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:336 index.docbook:348 index.docbook:362
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Type <userinput>3000</userinput> and press the <guibutton>¥</guibutton> "
"button or the <keycap>Y</keycap> key."
msgstr ""
"Ukucajte <userinput>3000</userinput> i pritisnite <guibutton>¥</guibutton> "
"dugme ili <keycap>Y</keycap> tipku."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:338 index.docbook:351 index.docbook:365
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter <userinput>20</userinput> and press the <guibutton>%</guibutton> "
"button or the <keycap>%</keycap> key. As with multiplications, the value had "
"to be typed <emphasis>before</emphasis> the percentage."
msgstr ""
"Unesite <userinput>20</userinput> i pritisnite <guibutton>%</guibutton> "
"dugme ili <keycap>%</keycap> tipku. Kao kod množenja, vrijednost mora biti "
"ukucana <emphasis>prije</emphasis> procenta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:341
#, no-c-format
msgid "Look at the result: it is equivalent to 600 yen."
msgstr "Pogledajte rezultat: jednak je 600 jena."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:345
#, no-c-format
msgid "How much is 3000 yen plus 20%?"
msgstr "Koliko je 3000 jena plus 20%?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:350
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press the <guibutton>+</guibutton> button or the <keycap>+</keycap> key."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite <guibutton>+</guibutton> dugme ili <keycap>+</keycap> tipku."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:354
#, no-c-format
msgid "Look at the result: 26.96 € or 3600 ¥ at the time of writing."
msgstr "Pogledajte rezultat: 26.96 € ili 3600 ¥ u vrijeme pisanja."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:359
#, no-c-format
msgid "How much is 3000 yen minus 20%?"
msgstr "Koliko je 3000 jena minus 20%?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:364
#, no-c-format
msgid "Press the <guibutton>-</guibutton> button or <keycap>-</keycap> key."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite <guibutton>-</guibutton> dugme ili <keycap>-</keycap> tipku."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:368
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Look at the result: 17.97 € or 2400 ¥ at the date of writing these lines."
msgstr "Pogledajte rezultat: 17.97 € ili 2400 ¥ na dan pisanja ove linije."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:375
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using Intermediate Memory"
msgstr "Korištenje posredne memorije"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:378
#, no-c-format
msgid "How do I store now and recall later some value?"
msgstr "Kako da sada pohranim i poslije ponovno pozovem neke vrijednosti?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:379
#, no-c-format
msgid "Do your computations."
msgstr "Obavite svoje proračune."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:380
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press <guibutton>Min</guibutton> (Memory in) button to store the value in "
"the <guilabel>Result</guilabel> area. Please notice that the other memory "
"keys now become available."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite <guibutton>Min</guibutton> (Memory in) dugme kako biste pohranili "
"vrijednost iz <guilabel>Rezultat</guilabel> područja. Molim vas da "
"primjetite kako sada ostale memorijske tipke postaju dostupne."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:383
#, no-c-format
msgid "Do some other work with the calculator."
msgstr "Obavite još neke poslove s kalkulatorom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:384
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Recall the value from the memory by pressing the <guibutton>MR</guibutton> "
"(Memory Recall) button."
msgstr ""
"Ponovno pozovite vrijednost iz memorije pritiskom na <guibutton>MR</"
"guibutton> (Memory Recall) dugme."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:388
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Internally, the values are recalled with no unit or in the reference "
"currency (euro) with the maximum precision allowed by the mathematical "
"library. In some rare cases, this might lead to rounding problems if the "
"stored value is a rounded value in a non-reference currency."
msgstr ""
"Interno, vrijednosti se pozivaju bez jedinice ili u referentnoj valuti "
"(euro) uz maksimalnu preciznost dozvoljenu od strane matematičke biblioteke. "
"U nekim rijetkim slučajevima, to može dovesti do problema sa zaokruživanjem "
"ukoliko je pohranjena vrijednost zaokružena u valuti koja nije referentna."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:395
#, no-c-format
msgid "How do I clear the memory?"
msgstr "Kako čistim memoriju?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:396
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press the <guibutton>Reset</guibutton> button. Please notice that the "
"<guibutton>Reset</guibutton> clears everything: the input, the result and "
"the memory."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite <guibutton>Reset</guibutton> dugme. Primijetite da "
"<guibutton>Reset</guibutton> čisti sve: ulaz, rezultat i memoriju."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:402
#, no-c-format
msgid "How do I compute 3.1 * 5.2 € + 2.7 * 8.9 €?"
msgstr "Kako da izračunam 3.1 * 5.2 € + 2.7 * 8.9 €?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:403 index.docbook:415
#, no-c-format
msgid "First compute the first half: <userinput>3.1 * 5.2 €</userinput>."
msgstr "Prvo izračunajte prvu polovinu: <userinput>3.1 * 5.2 €</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:404 index.docbook:416
#, no-c-format
msgid "Store the result in memory with <guibutton>Min</guibutton> button."
msgstr "Pohranite rezultat u memoriju sa <guibutton>Min</guibutton> dugmetom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:405 index.docbook:417
#, no-c-format
msgid "Now compute the other half: <userinput>2.7 * 8.9 €</userinput>."
msgstr "Sada izračunajte drugu polovinu: <userinput>2.7 * 8.9 €</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:406
#, no-c-format
msgid "Add the result to the memory with <guibutton>M+</guibutton> button."
msgstr "Dodajte rezultat u memoriju pomoću <guibutton>M+</guibutton> dugmeta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:407 index.docbook:419
#, no-c-format
msgid "Recall the sum with <guibutton>MR</guibutton> button."
msgstr "Pozovite sumu pomoću <guibutton>MR</guibutton> dugmeta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:410
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are other solutions like <userinput>3.1 * 5.2 € Min 2.7 * 8.9 € + MR</"
"userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Postoje i druga rješenja, kao <userinput>3.1 * 5.2 € Min 2.7 * 8.9 € + MR</"
"userinput>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:414
#, no-c-format
msgid "How do I compute 3.1 * 5.2 € - 2.7 * 8.9 €?"
msgstr "Kako ću izračunati 3.1 * 5.2 € - 2.7 * 8.9 €?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:418
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Subtract the result from the memory with <guibutton>M-</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Oduzmite rezultat od vrijednosti u memoriji sa <guibutton>M-</guibutton> "
"dugmetom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:422
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The sequence <userinput>3.1 * 5.2 € Min 2.7 * 8.9 € - MR</userinput> "
"computes the difference in the reverse order."
msgstr ""
"Sekvenca <userinput>3.1 * 5.2 € Min 2.7 * 8.9 € - MR</userinput> računa "
"razliku u obrnutom redoslijedu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:429
#, no-c-format
msgid "Command Reference"
msgstr "Komandna obavijest"

