msgstr "Prikaz <guilabel>About</guilabel> boxa"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:532
#, no-c-format
msgid "Help"
msgstr "Pomoć"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:533
#, no-c-format
msgid "Displays these help pages"
msgstr "Prikaz ovih stranica"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:535
#, no-c-format
msgid "The drop down list with currency codes and names"
msgstr "Lista sa kodovima i imenima valuta"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:536
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selects an other currency to work with"
msgstr "Odabir druge valute za rad"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:542
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Settings Dialog"
msgstr "Dijalog postavki"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:549
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reference currency, rates origin"
msgstr "Referentna valuta, osnova za cijene"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:551
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This setting defines from where &keurocalc; should download the exchange "
"rates between the reference currency and other currencies. The following "
"choices are available:"
msgstr ""
"Ova postavka određuje odakle bi &keurocalc; trebao skinuti kurseve među "
"referentnom i ostalim valutama. Slijedeći odabiri su dostupni:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:558
#, no-c-format
msgid "Euro, no network access (fixed rates only)"
msgstr "Euro, bez pristupa mreži (samo fiksne stope)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:560
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Euro is the reference currency. No variable rate is downloaded or used. The "
"only available currencies are the ones that have a fixed conversion rate "
"with the euro."
msgstr ""
"Euro je referentna valuta. Nijedna stopa nije preuzeta ili korištena. Jedine "
"dostupne valute su one koje imaju fiksnu stopu konverzije sa eurom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:563
#, no-c-format
msgid "This setting is adapted to computers with no network access."
msgstr "Ova postavka je prilagođena računarima bez pristupa internetu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:568
#, no-c-format
msgid "Euro, European Central Bank"
msgstr "Euro, European Central Bank"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:570
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Euro is the reference currency. The fixed exchange rates are available. "
"&keurocalc; attempts to download the variable rates from the <ulink url="
"\"http://www.ecb.int/stats/eurofxref/\">European Central Bank (ECB)</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Euro je referentna valuta. Stope fiksnog kursa su dostupne. &keurocalc; "
"pokušava skinuti kurs sa <ulink url=\"http://www.ecb.int/stats/eurofxref/"
"\">European Central Bank (ECB)</ulink>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:591
#, no-c-format
msgid "Euro, Time Genie"
msgstr "Euro, Time Genie"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:593
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Euro is the reference currency. The fixed exchange rates are available. "
"&keurocalc; attempts to download the variable rates from the <ulink url="
"\"http://rss.timegenie.com/foreign_exchange_rates_forex\">Time Genie (TG)</"
"ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Euro je referentna valuta. Stope fiksnog kursa su dostupne. &keurocalc; "
"pokušava skinuti kurs sa  <ulink url=\"http://rss.timegenie.com/"
"foreign_exchange_rates_forex\">Time Genie (TG)</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:604
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default currency"
msgstr "Podrazumijevana valuta"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:606
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This setting defines the other currency that is used when &keurocalc; starts "
"up or when the user validates the new settings."
msgstr ""
"Ova postavka definiše drugu valutu koja se koristi kada se &keurocalc; "
"pokrene ili kada korisnik podesi nove postavke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:609
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Notice that the selected currency might not be provided by the selected "
"rates source. In that case, the first available currency in the list is used."
msgstr ""
"Obratite pažnju da odabrana valuta možda nije podržana od strane odabranog "
"izvora stopa. U tom slučaju se koristi prva dostupna valuta na listi."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:615
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rounding"
msgstr "Zaokruživanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:617
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This setting defines how the results should be presented in the display "
"area. Internally, all computations are done with the precision offered by "
"the mathematical library, but it usually makes no sense presenting tenths of "
"cents. The following rounding methods are available:"
msgstr ""
"Ova postavka određuje kako rezultati trebaju biti predstavljeni na zaslonu. "
"Interno, svi proračuni se obavljaju s preciznošću koju nudi matematička "
"biblioteka, ali obično nema smisla predstavljati desetine centi. Sljedeće "
"metode zaokruživanja su dostupne:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:624
#, no-c-format
msgid "Official rounding rules"
msgstr "Zvanična pravila zaokruživanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:626
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The EU conversion rules or other official conversion rules are used. It "
"means that the result is rounded to the next unit for currencies like the "
"Japanese yen or the Italian lira, and rounded to the next hundredth of unit "
"(<quote>cents</quote>) for currencies like the euro or the dollar."
msgstr ""
"Koriste se EU pravila konverzije ili druga zvanična pravila konverzije. To "
"znači da se rezultat zaokružuje na sljedeću jedinicu za valute kao što je "
"japanski jen ili italijanski lira, i zaokružuje se na sljedeću stotinku "
"jedinice (<quote>centi</quote>) za valute poput eura ili dolara."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:630
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For example, 158.323 yen would be rounded to 158 yen. 12.537 euro would be "
"rounded to 12.54 euro."
msgstr ""
"Naprimjer, 158.323 jena bi bilo zaokruženo na 158 jena. 12.537 eura bi bilo "
"zaokruženo na 12.54 eura."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:636
#, no-c-format
msgid "Smallest coin method"
msgstr "Metoda najmanjeg novičića"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:638
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The result is rounded to the next value of the smallest coin that circulates "
"in the country that uses that currency. For disappeared currencies like the "
"Italian lira, it uses the smallest coin that used to circulate before the "
"currency has been withdrawn: in the case of the Italian lira, it was the 50 "
"liras coin."
msgstr ""
"Rezultat se zaokružuje na sljedeću vrijednost najmanjeg novčića koja "
"cirkuliše u zemlji koja koristi tu valutu. Za nestale valute poput "
"talijanske lira, koristi se najmanji novčić koji je cirkulisao prije nego je "
"valuta povučena: u slučaju italijanske lira, to je bilo novčić od 50 lira."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:643
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For example, 1235.9 Italian liras would be rounded to 1250 liras. 39.45 "
"Norwegian crowns would be rounded to 39.50 crowns."
msgstr ""
"Naprimjer, 1235.9 talijanskih lira bilo bi zaokruženo na 1250 lira. 39.45 "
"norveška kruna bi bila zaokružena na 39.50 kruna."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:645
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"We lack information about the smallest coins that exist in every country. "
"Please send a bug report if &keurocalc; uses an incorrect value for the "
"smallest available coin in your country, and we will enter that information."
msgstr ""
"Nedostaje mi informacija o najmanjim kovanicama koje su postojale u svakoj "
"zemlji. Molimo vas da pošaljite izvještaj o grešci ako &keurocalc; koristi "
"pogrešnu vrijednost za najmanji novčić dostupan u vašoj zemlji, i mi ćemo "
"unijeti te informacije."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:652
#, no-c-format
msgid "No rounding at all"
msgstr "Bez ikakvog zaokruživanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:654
#, no-c-format
msgid "The computed value is displayed unchanged, as a floating point number."
msgstr ""
"Izračunate vrijednosti se prikazuju nepromijenjene, kao broj s pomičnim "
"zarezom."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:663
#, no-c-format
msgid "Look and feel"
msgstr "Pogledaj i osjeti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:665
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This setting defines the appearance and behavior of &keurocalc;. The "
"following options are available:"
msgstr ""
"Ova postavka određuje izgled i ponašanje &keurocalc;. Dostupne su slijedeće "
"opcije:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:670
#, no-c-format
msgid "Display color"
msgstr "Boja zaslona"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:672
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The background color of the display areas (both input and result). To change "
"the background color, click on <guibutton>Change...</guibutton>. This opens "
"the standard &kde; color selection dialog. Choose a new color, then press "
"<guibutton>OK</guibutton> to validate the new choice."
msgstr ""
"Pozadinska boja područja zaslona (i ulaz i rezultat). Kako biste promijenili "
"boju pozadine, pritisnite <guibutton>Promijeni...</guibutton>. Ovo otvara "
"uobičajni &kde; dijalog za odabir boje. Odaberite novu boju, onda pritisnite "
"<guibutton>OK</guibutton> kako biste potvrdili svoj odabir."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:680
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable splash screen"
msgstr "Uključi pozdravni ekran"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:682
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Uncheck this box if you do not want to initial picture to appear when "
"&keurocalc; starts."
msgstr ""
"Poništite ovaj box ako ne želite da se početna slika pojavi kada se "
"&keurocalc; pokrene."

